    "---\n",
    "## 📝 Notes & Next Steps\n",
    "\n",
    "### Thresholds (adjust in `CONFIG` or `MY_CONFIG`)\n",
    "| Key | Default | Description |\n",
    "|-----|---------|-------------|\n",
    "| `C_min_eps_growth` | 25% | Quarterly EPS growth YoY |\n",
    "| `A_min_annual_eps_growth` | 25% | Annual EPS growth (3-yr avg) |\n",
    "| `N_near_high_pct` | 10% | Max % below 52-week high |\n",
    "| `S_min_ud_ratio` | 1.0 | Up/down volume ratio |\n",
    "| `L_min_rs_rating` | 70 | Relative strength rating |\n",
    "| `M_spy_above_ma_days` | 50 | SPY MA lookback days |\n",
    "\n",
    "### Potential improvements\n",
    "- [ ] Add IBD-style Composite Rating (C + A + L weighted)\n",
    "- [ ] Screen by industry group rank (using sector ETFs)\n",
    "- [ ] Integrate with `options_scanner.py` for trade signals\n",
    "- [ ] Streamlit web UI for mobile access\n",
    "- [ ] Schedule via GitHub Actions (daily scan)\n",
    "- [ ] Alert via email/SMS when new stock hits 6/7 or 7/7\n",
    "\n",
    "### Limitations\n",
    "- EPS data quality depends on yfinance (may vary by ticker)\n",
    "- RS Rating is a proxy — not identical to IBD's proprietary formula\n",
    "- Industry group ranking is simplified (uses sector, not 197 IBD groups)\n",
    "- Not financial advice — always do your own due diligence"
   ],
